title: Didn't get corruption Icon
body:
Hello all,
     Saw the new dark star 'corruption icon' and thought it looked pretty sick. So i added two people to my friends list and then won a game of dark star with them. I did not ,however, get the icon. Have I made a mistake or done something wrong? Thank-you for your help!

replies.body: Yeah me too I played this game mode with 2 of my freinds and got a win but never recieved the icon for doing it can you guys check if I did anything wrong plz
Just got my icon on the 29th like clockwork a couple of days ago, did you get yours?

No worries! Those [**Dark Star icons**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/learn-more-about-dark-star-2017) are still in the process of going out, but if you don't have yours by 5/29 then go ahead and reach out to us in a ticket at that point.
